OL,3,CWoman killed in Talbot Green shooting
OL,4,Cdied of injuries to heart and lung
OL,6,FA 40-year-old woman who was shot in
OL,7,Fthe chest at an address in Talbot
OL,8,FGreen, Rhondda Cynon Taf, died of
OL,9,Finjuries to her heart and lung, the
OL,10,Fopening of an inquest has been told.
OL,12,FJoanne Penney died after being shot at
OL,13,Fan address in Llys Illtyd in Talbot
OL,14,FGreen on Sunday, 9 March.
OL,16,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,17,Fto find Ms Penney with serious
OL,18,Finjuries and she was pronounced dead.
OL,20,FSix people have been charged in
OL,21,Fconnection with her death.
