OL,6,FBeverley Morgan, coroner's officer,
OL,7,Ftold an inquest opening at South Wales
OL,8,FCentral Coroner's Court in Pontypridd
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, 25 March, that a post-
OL,10,Fmortem investigation had provided the
OL,11,Fprovisional cause of death as "gunshot
OL,12,Fwound to the left chest involving the
OL,13,Fheart and left lung".
OL,15,FShe added: "At 18.10 hours on Sunday,
OL,16,FMarch 9, 2025, South Wales Police were
OL,17,Fnotified of a reported shooting at
OL,18,FGreen Park, Talbot Green.
