OL,6,F"On arrival of emergency services,
OL,7,Fthey found Joanne Penney lying on her
OL,8,Fback unresponsive in the living room
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,F"She had sustained a gunshot wound to
OL,12,Fthe chest. Despite efforts of
OL,13,Femergency services, she was later
OL,14,Fpronounced deceased."
OL,16,FGraeme Hughes, senior coroner for
OL,17,FSouth Wales Central, adjourned the
OL,18,Finquest for further police
OL,19,Finvestigations to be carried out.
