OL,6,FHe said: "Based on that evidence I
OL,7,Fhave sufficient reason to suspect that
OL,8,FMs Penney's death was due to violence,
OL,9,Fso I am duty-bound to continue the
OL,10,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,11,Fsurrounding her death.
OL,13,F"However, I am cognisant that
OL,14,Findividuals have been arrested and
OL,15,Fcharged and so I will suspend this
OL,16,Finvestigation pending the conclusion
OL,17,Fof those criminal proceedings.
OL,19,F"I wish to pass on my own condolences
OL,20,Fto Ms Penney's family and friends."
