OL,6,FFollowing the incident, five people -
OL,7,Ftwo from Cardiff and three from
OL,8,FLeicestershire - have been charged
OL,9,Fwith murder, and one person from
OL,10,FLeicestershire has been charged with
OL,11,Fassisting an offender.
OL,13,FA trial date has been set for October
OL,14,F20, with proceedings expected to last
OL,15,Fsix to eight weeks.
