OL,6,FIn a tribute, Ms Penney's family
OL,7,Fpreviously said: "We are devastated by
OL,8,Fthe tragic loss of our beloved Joanne.
OL,9,FShe was a daughter, mother, sister and
OL,10,Fniece ` loved deeply by all who knew
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,F"Her kindness, strength and love for
OL,14,Fher family will never be forgotten.
OL,15,FDuring this incredibly difficult time,
OL,16,Fwe ask for privacy as we grieve and
OL,17,Fbegin to process this unimaginable
OL,18,Floss."
